I"’<p><a href="https://www.archlinux.org/">Arch Linux</a> is a lightweight and flexible Linux distribution for x86_64.</p>
<p>Install the needed Python packages.</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">sudo pacman -S python
sudo pacman -S python-pip
</code></pre>
<p>From here on, we recommend you to follow the
<a href="https://www.home-assistant.io/docs/installation/virtualenv/">virtualenv</a> guide.</p>
